WEBVTT

01:52.009 --> 01:57.710
[The Legend of Rosy Clouds]

01:58.479 --> 02:01.910
[Episode 9]

02:02.240 --> 02:03.730
It seems you are

02:03.760 --> 02:05.160
in a very good mood today.

02:05.680 --> 02:06.140
This...

02:06.480 --> 02:08.100
is all thanks to you.

02:08.310 --> 02:09.910
Do you know that

02:09.910 --> 02:11.640
I almost got heatstroke today?

02:13.000 --> 02:13.960
Your Excellency,

02:13.960 --> 02:15.420
I've finally understood.

02:15.730 --> 02:17.910
You must have thought
I earned that 500 gold

02:17.910 --> 02:19.340
too easily.

02:19.370 --> 02:22.700
You deliberately made things
difficult for me, didn't you?

02:24.790 --> 02:25.770
If you beg me,

02:26.310 --> 02:27.520
arranging some easy tasks for you

02:27.520 --> 02:28.579
isn't impossible.

02:32.910 --> 02:34.680
More tasks?

02:35.590 --> 02:36.700
What tasks?

02:41.400 --> 02:42.079
Tell me.

02:43.430 --> 02:45.360
I just remembered that
when I was at Huan'e House,

02:45.360 --> 02:46.620
I lost a handkerchief.

02:47.240 --> 02:49.440
How about you embroider a new one for me?

02:50.030 --> 02:51.000
A handkerchief?

02:53.060 --> 02:54.579
For your handkerchief,

02:54.610 --> 02:56.870
just have the embroiderers
at the Tailoring Bureau make it.

02:56.870 --> 02:58.150
Why must I do it?

02:58.710 --> 02:59.770
That's different.

03:01.560 --> 03:03.220
What's so different about it?

03:05.710 --> 03:06.960
It just is.

03:08.080 --> 03:09.120
It's the same.

03:17.920 --> 03:19.000
However...

03:19.910 --> 03:20.910
Your Excellency,

03:20.910 --> 03:23.560
if you insist on my embroidering
a handkerchief for you,

03:23.560 --> 03:24.760
it's not impossible.

03:25.710 --> 03:27.120
It's just that...

03:31.000 --> 03:31.960
Just what?

03:33.870 --> 03:34.800
It's just that

03:34.800 --> 03:35.870
we need to discuss

03:35.870 --> 03:37.329
the selection exam again.

03:38.180 --> 03:38.950
No way.

03:40.250 --> 03:41.290
Why not?

03:41.400 --> 03:42.400
Your Excellency.

03:43.430 --> 03:45.900
Young Master Lou Qiyan from Juyun Pavilion
has arrived.

03:45.900 --> 03:47.140
Young Master Qiyan?

03:47.170 --> 03:49.170
Let him wait in the Huiyun Pavilion.

03:49.430 --> 03:50.030
Yes.

03:52.079 --> 03:53.310
Lou Qiyan?

03:54.560 --> 03:56.000
You summoned him?

03:58.750 --> 04:01.000
Wei and Yan failed
to get the blueprints from him.

04:01.000 --> 04:03.000
Naturally, I have to meet him myself.

04:03.000 --> 04:03.560
You,

04:04.030 --> 04:05.090
get some good rest.

04:05.470 --> 04:05.960
Also,

04:06.400 --> 04:08.800
don't even think about the selection exam.

04:09.360 --> 04:10.360
Go back and rest.

04:11.620 --> 04:12.360
Your Excellency,

04:12.360 --> 04:13.490
I want to go with you.

04:14.750 --> 04:16.010
What are you going for?

04:16.310 --> 04:17.959
You are the esteemed lady.

04:18.120 --> 04:19.480
Of course, you can't go.

04:20.570 --> 04:21.570
Your Excellency,

04:21.680 --> 04:23.040
I can disguise myself as a personal guard

04:23.040 --> 04:24.390
and go in with you.

04:24.390 --> 04:25.000
Right?

04:25.560 --> 04:26.240
No.

04:27.790 --> 04:29.060
I'll embroider the handkerchief for you.

04:29.060 --> 04:29.920
In your dreams.

04:31.350 --> 04:32.180
Your Excellency,

04:32.180 --> 04:33.620
just let me go with you

04:33.650 --> 04:35.180
and hear what's going on.

04:35.240 --> 04:36.090
Please?

04:41.880 --> 04:42.940
Hide in the corner.

04:43.159 --> 04:44.040
No eye contact.

04:44.430 --> 04:45.600
Not even a glance.

04:48.360 --> 04:49.310
I promise.

04:56.930 --> 04:59.159
His Excellency is here!

05:27.510 --> 05:28.720
Your Excellency, may I ask why you

05:28.720 --> 05:29.920
have summoned me?

05:30.430 --> 05:31.390
I heard

05:32.040 --> 05:34.100
you only do business with one person.

05:34.600 --> 05:36.170
One channel, one person.

05:36.480 --> 05:38.010
This is my rule in business.

05:38.390 --> 05:39.990
No matter how big the deal is,

05:40.140 --> 05:41.650
I won't do it.

05:42.680 --> 05:43.720
Are you saying

05:44.550 --> 05:45.700
not even me?

05:47.600 --> 05:49.530
If Her Ladyship comes to talk to me,

05:50.120 --> 05:51.120
maybe it'll work.

05:53.690 --> 05:56.220
Do you think you can see her
whenever you want?

05:58.409 --> 05:59.880
Aren't you afraid I'll punish you

05:59.880 --> 06:01.740
for disrespecting the Governor?

06:03.330 --> 06:05.210
It seems you don't welcome me.

06:07.270 --> 06:08.530
I'll take my leave now.

06:33.670 --> 06:34.770
If I've offended you,

06:34.770 --> 06:36.770
please calm down, Your Excellency.

06:49.800 --> 06:51.400
For making you unhappy,

06:51.680 --> 06:53.050
I am truly terrified.

06:56.830 --> 06:58.230
I will excuse myself now.

07:06.340 --> 07:07.660
Your beard fell off.

07:48.740 --> 07:51.880
♪ Watch how many flowers
bloom and wither ♪

07:52.300 --> 07:55.730
♪ Count how many springs
and autumns pass ♪

07:56.100 --> 07:58.659
♪ Why the sighs and regrets? ♪

08:04.720 --> 08:08.210
♪ Lovers wait a lifetime ♪

08:08.630 --> 08:11.820
♪ Feelings that can't be severed ♪

08:12.300 --> 08:15.050
♪ How to let go? ♪

08:20.960 --> 08:24.310
♪ All our fates were long inscribed ♪

08:24.650 --> 08:28.310
♪ How to set free grief and joy? ♪

08:28.880 --> 08:30.600
♪ Mortal life is but an ephemeral dream ♪

08:31.010 --> 08:36.559
♪ No mortal soul may rule its life ♪

08:36.940 --> 08:38.429
♪ If women are akin to blossoms ♪

08:38.470 --> 08:40.809
♪ Can they be cherished tenderly? ♪

08:40.970 --> 08:44.140
♪ For whom do they hide tears silently? ♪

08:44.420 --> 08:46.640
♪ How could one bear to lay blame? ♪

08:46.660 --> 08:49.030
♪ Time runs wild with reckless haste ♪

08:49.060 --> 08:52.760
♪ Never mind that
fate dyes pureness crimson red ♪

08:53.070 --> 08:54.410
♪ For whom does ♪

08:54.430 --> 08:56.600
♪ This phoenix blossom bloom? ♪

08:56.630 --> 09:00.600
♪ Love fills my years,
and my heart remains true ♪

08:56.870 --> 08:57.870
Your Excellency.

09:00.830 --> 09:02.880
♪ Let all worldly longing fade away ♪

09:02.910 --> 09:05.300
♪ Fall deep within a single dream ♪

09:05.470 --> 09:13.100
♪ Wait till a breath of wind arrives ♪

09:07.440 --> 09:08.240
Look.

09:20.420 --> 09:22.750
The 24 types of pastries offered this time

09:22.970 --> 09:25.300
correspond exactly to the 24 solar terms.

09:25.840 --> 09:26.960
This uses the ancient method

09:26.960 --> 09:28.710
to commemorate those meritorious subjects

09:28.710 --> 09:29.980
and signifies that

09:30.200 --> 09:31.400
our great Nine Cities

09:31.480 --> 09:32.600
will have good weather

09:32.600 --> 09:34.440
and grow stronger year by year.

09:39.840 --> 09:41.670
As for Lord Zheng,

09:42.150 --> 09:43.510
although

09:43.870 --> 09:45.340
he is a bit conservative,

09:46.110 --> 09:47.060
he

09:47.080 --> 09:48.320
truly wants

09:48.390 --> 09:50.190
what's best for the Nine Cities.

09:50.670 --> 09:52.240
I don't know if doing this

09:53.030 --> 09:54.510
can really move him.

09:56.290 --> 09:57.470
Actually, agreeing to

09:57.470 --> 09:59.070
repair the ancestral temple

09:59.670 --> 10:00.670
isn't

10:00.800 --> 10:02.370
entirely for Mr. Zheng.

10:05.080 --> 10:06.080
Your Excellency,

10:06.080 --> 10:06.750
I think...

10:08.110 --> 10:08.960
I...

10:10.820 --> 10:11.820
I...

10:14.200 --> 10:14.930
Forget it.

10:15.010 --> 10:16.390
Let's talk somewhere else.

10:16.390 --> 10:16.870
Where to?

10:16.870 --> 10:17.670
Follow me.

10:17.670 --> 10:19.460
-Don't follow us!
-I can't wait!

10:19.460 --> 10:20.550
Can't wait?

10:24.560 --> 10:25.440
Don't laugh.

10:28.190 --> 10:29.920
What are you in such a hurry for?

10:30.660 --> 10:32.260
Come here, Your Excellency.

10:44.270 --> 10:45.270
Your Excellency.

10:45.650 --> 10:47.510
I need to ask you a question first.

10:48.790 --> 10:49.870
Tell me,

10:49.870 --> 10:52.330
are you satisfied
with the offering diagram

10:52.390 --> 10:53.870
I designed this time?

10:55.270 --> 10:56.240
It's not bad.

10:58.510 --> 11:00.360
Then does this count as me

11:00.360 --> 11:01.840
successfully completing

11:01.840 --> 11:03.100
the task you gave me?

11:05.790 --> 11:07.320
Compared to the past 2 days,

11:08.030 --> 11:09.360
your performance today

11:09.750 --> 11:10.610
is indeed good.

11:13.840 --> 11:14.600
Then...

11:15.150 --> 11:15.720
then...

11:16.560 --> 11:17.760
is there a reward?

11:22.510 --> 11:23.600
Although...

11:24.790 --> 11:25.840
But...

11:27.460 --> 11:29.260
Isn't this a bit inappropriate?

11:29.840 --> 11:30.510
What's...

11:31.480 --> 11:33.280
what's inappropriate about it?

11:34.730 --> 11:35.580
True.

11:36.290 --> 11:38.150
There's nothing inappropriate.

11:39.240 --> 11:40.170
Let's do it then.

11:44.240 --> 11:45.080
I...

11:45.110 --> 11:45.740
I...

11:46.460 --> 11:47.460
Your Excellency.

11:50.030 --> 11:51.030
Your Excellency.

11:51.090 --> 11:53.370
What are you doing?

11:55.150 --> 11:56.550
Didn't you want a reward?

11:59.080 --> 12:00.360
What I meant...

12:01.080 --> 12:02.000
was this.

12:04.730 --> 12:06.680
I wanted you to help review

12:07.300 --> 12:08.720
my examination script

12:09.060 --> 12:10.190
and assess my score.

12:17.530 --> 12:18.370
Will you?

12:19.240 --> 12:20.080
Let me see.

12:24.270 --> 12:25.120
This is...

12:25.620 --> 12:28.350
the exam paper
from the previous selection exam?

12:29.440 --> 12:30.500
Why did you do this?

12:30.960 --> 12:32.430
I want to...

12:33.200 --> 12:34.550
I... I want to...

12:35.440 --> 12:38.500
Of course, I want to participate
in the selection exam.

12:39.390 --> 12:41.320
The national selection exam is inevitable.

12:41.320 --> 12:43.250
Someone has to step forward first.

12:43.790 --> 12:44.600
And I...

12:45.150 --> 12:46.720
want to be the first to step forward

12:46.720 --> 12:47.980
to share your burdens.

12:48.670 --> 12:49.750
What do you think?

12:53.080 --> 12:54.010
Are you serious?

12:55.630 --> 12:56.160
Well,

12:56.180 --> 12:57.860
of course, I'm serious.

13:04.200 --> 13:06.430
Women of the inner court
can't interfere in politics.

13:06.430 --> 13:07.320
As my wife,

13:08.040 --> 13:10.640
even a national selection exam
is not allowed.

13:13.070 --> 13:13.980
Well,

13:14.600 --> 13:16.060
I naturally know.

13:16.870 --> 13:17.960
But...

13:19.320 --> 13:20.980
I've already thought of a way.

13:21.750 --> 13:22.600
What way?

13:23.120 --> 13:23.960
Divorce.

13:28.840 --> 13:29.480
What?

13:30.240 --> 13:31.630
Divorce.

13:32.400 --> 13:33.160
Look,

13:33.190 --> 13:34.120
we get a divorce,

13:34.140 --> 13:35.260
and I take the exam.

13:35.290 --> 13:36.820
Everything will be solved.

13:37.640 --> 13:38.330
Right?

13:40.360 --> 13:41.030
Look,

13:41.750 --> 13:42.460
you were

13:42.480 --> 13:43.970
forced to marry me.

13:44.260 --> 13:46.660
And I'm your wife in name only.

13:48.720 --> 13:49.840
Why not?

13:51.890 --> 13:52.820
What did you say?

13:54.840 --> 13:55.440
Nothing.

13:56.090 --> 13:56.690
Continue.

13:59.750 --> 14:01.280
Here's what I was thinking.

14:01.350 --> 14:02.860
I originally thought

14:02.990 --> 14:04.320
the two of us

14:04.880 --> 14:06.960
could put on an act for a year or two.

14:07.360 --> 14:09.610
By then, I won't have borne any children.

14:09.610 --> 14:10.970
So for the sake of heirs,

14:11.000 --> 14:12.600
we won't even need to say a word.

14:12.600 --> 14:13.320
Lord Lyu and the others

14:13.320 --> 14:15.320
will naturally force us to divorce.

14:15.510 --> 14:17.200
But right now...

14:17.200 --> 14:18.030
You're right.

14:19.680 --> 14:21.080
It's in name only anyway.

14:22.840 --> 14:24.300
Isn't it just for 500 gold?

14:25.500 --> 14:26.140
I...

14:27.510 --> 14:28.840
I see it's getting late.

14:29.530 --> 14:30.590
Tomorrow morning,

14:30.670 --> 14:32.380
I'll have to go to the Zheng Residence.

14:32.380 --> 14:33.190
Rest early.

14:35.750 --> 14:36.360
Your Excellency.

14:36.360 --> 14:37.760
-No need to see me out.
-Your...

14:37.760 --> 14:40.000
Y-You haven't answered me yet.

14:40.140 --> 14:41.870
Are we getting a divorce or not?

14:44.480 --> 14:45.410
Tomorrow,

14:45.430 --> 14:47.230
I'll wait for you to come find me!

14:52.980 --> 14:54.340
Isn't my idea

14:54.480 --> 14:55.910
pretty good?

15:01.810 --> 15:02.810
Miss,

15:02.840 --> 15:03.750
you haven't slept for nights

15:03.750 --> 15:05.360
studying the sacrificial offerings

15:05.360 --> 15:06.870
with Her Ladyship.

15:07.480 --> 15:08.910
If the Master finds out,

15:08.910 --> 15:10.240
he will be heartbroken.

15:11.990 --> 15:12.990
He deserves it.

15:13.010 --> 15:15.270
Who asked him to send me to the residence?

15:16.510 --> 15:17.320
But now,

15:17.320 --> 15:19.000
for the man in the Guardian Corps camp,

15:19.000 --> 15:20.740
you wish you could just live there.

15:20.740 --> 15:21.810
Miss,

15:21.840 --> 15:22.550
in my opinion,

15:22.550 --> 15:23.880
he won't appreciate it.

15:24.230 --> 15:25.320
Just like last time,

15:25.320 --> 15:27.520
for the plum juice
you made for him yourself,

15:27.520 --> 15:29.730
he just threw your kindness
back in your face.

15:29.730 --> 15:30.570
In my opinion,

15:30.600 --> 15:31.660
you should just...

15:49.030 --> 15:51.050
It's all my fault
for being so clumsy last time.

15:51.050 --> 15:52.630
His Guardian Corps

15:52.900 --> 15:54.010
got nosebleeds from drinking it.

15:54.010 --> 15:55.670
Good thing he didn't drink it.

15:55.800 --> 15:56.850
Miss,

15:56.880 --> 15:58.680
how did you hurt your hand again?

15:59.200 --> 16:01.840
Your wound from yesterday
hasn't even healed yet.

16:01.840 --> 16:02.720
It's fine.

16:02.720 --> 16:04.620
The injuries from my fights
with Wei Rong were worse than this.

16:04.620 --> 16:05.020
Look,

16:05.040 --> 16:06.640
isn't it perfectly fine now?

16:07.080 --> 16:07.610
Let's go.

16:09.630 --> 16:10.830
I'm sorry. I'm sorry.

16:15.140 --> 16:16.050
Miss,

16:16.080 --> 16:18.240
let's not suffer like that again
next time.

16:18.240 --> 16:19.200
When you're in the residence,

16:19.200 --> 16:21.200
you've never done this kind of work.

16:22.040 --> 16:22.760
Careful.

16:29.150 --> 16:31.280
This is a premium medicine for wounds.

16:32.670 --> 16:35.000
At least, Wei Ying has a conscience.

16:49.000 --> 16:49.750
Master,

16:50.440 --> 16:53.440
His Excellency has personally
come here to visit you.

17:05.990 --> 17:06.740
Elder Zheng.

17:10.720 --> 17:12.810
Please forgive me for being unwell

17:12.839 --> 17:14.400
and unable to get up.

17:14.930 --> 17:16.109
Your health is the most important.

17:16.109 --> 17:17.510
No need for formalities.

17:18.079 --> 17:20.040
I heard you were unwell,

17:20.060 --> 17:21.660
so I specially came to visit.

17:22.829 --> 17:24.540
Seeing you bedridden now,

17:26.150 --> 17:27.910
I am deeply worried.

17:27.930 --> 17:30.280
I am just an old bag of bones.

17:31.830 --> 17:33.020
I am fortunate

17:33.470 --> 17:35.510
to have your concern.

17:38.220 --> 17:39.180
Take it easy.

17:41.290 --> 17:42.090
Elder Zheng,

17:42.770 --> 17:43.580
on this trip,

17:43.870 --> 17:45.130
besides visiting you,

17:45.570 --> 17:46.900
there is one more thing.

17:49.320 --> 17:51.980
I am here to apologize
to you on behalf of Fan Yun.

17:57.610 --> 18:01.740
This is the sacrificial text for
breaking ground at the ancestral temple.

18:02.580 --> 18:05.020
Fan Yun will focus on
the residence's affairs in the future.

18:05.020 --> 18:06.760
Nine Cities can't do without you.

18:06.760 --> 18:08.360
Thank you, Your Excellency.

18:15.770 --> 18:17.130
Before coming to here,

18:17.720 --> 18:19.500
I went to take a look
at the ancestral temple.

18:19.500 --> 18:20.840
The repair project

18:20.870 --> 18:22.190
is mostly completed.

18:22.880 --> 18:23.780
I was thinking,

18:24.160 --> 18:26.160
once you recover from your illness,

18:26.350 --> 18:29.680
you can personally preside over
the sacrificial ceremony.

18:30.520 --> 18:31.740
Along the way,

18:31.830 --> 18:32.990
I was reminded of

18:33.550 --> 18:35.410
when the late governor was alive.

18:35.920 --> 18:39.170
You led troops to fight fierce battles
with Zhuiyue City for 3 years.

18:39.170 --> 18:40.570
In the bitter cold lands,

18:40.680 --> 18:42.140
you contracted a disease.

18:42.480 --> 18:43.610
Thirteen years ago,

18:44.160 --> 18:45.440
during the rebellion for the throne,

18:45.440 --> 18:48.240
you wiped out the remnants
of the rebel ministers.

18:48.300 --> 18:50.560
That's why we have the Nine Cities today.

18:51.310 --> 18:51.720
I have always

18:51.720 --> 18:53.950
kept in mind the efforts you have devoted

18:53.950 --> 18:55.880
all these years to the Nine Cities.

19:01.370 --> 19:04.320
[Zheng Residence]

19:01.870 --> 19:03.420
You must rest well

19:03.440 --> 19:04.430
and recover soon.

19:04.430 --> 19:05.780
Thank you, Your Excellency.

19:05.780 --> 19:06.910
No need to see me out.

19:33.920 --> 19:36.220
Congratulations
on your smooth return, Master.

19:36.220 --> 19:36.880
Everything

19:36.960 --> 19:38.480
is back to normal.

19:42.810 --> 19:44.040
Today, I

19:44.980 --> 19:46.050
drank the wine

19:46.440 --> 19:48.400
confusedly.

19:51.220 --> 19:52.070
How did I

19:52.550 --> 19:54.420
yield to him?

19:58.580 --> 20:00.540
The days ahead will be different.

20:02.770 --> 20:04.170
He can't touch me,

20:07.570 --> 20:10.130
and I can't touch him either.

20:21.400 --> 20:22.830
Such a good time

20:23.320 --> 20:24.350
makes me miss the days before,

20:24.350 --> 20:26.880
when I could frequently
leave the residence.

20:28.880 --> 20:30.200
But for you,

20:30.200 --> 20:31.540
being in the company of women
outside the residence

20:31.540 --> 20:33.600
is truly more interesting, isn't it?

20:35.810 --> 20:38.270
Try it, and you'll know
if it's interesting.

20:49.410 --> 20:51.540
-Your Excellency.
-Your Excellency.

20:54.620 --> 20:56.020
It's only just past noon.

20:56.400 --> 20:57.350
Why do you look

20:57.350 --> 20:58.300
unwell?

20:58.680 --> 21:00.680
I took a trip to the Zheng Residence.

21:01.250 --> 21:02.140
It seems

21:02.170 --> 21:03.430
it didn't go smoothly.

21:07.070 --> 21:08.440
It went pretty smoothly.

21:08.440 --> 21:10.040
Then why do you still look...

21:14.670 --> 21:16.230
Let me ask you a question.

21:16.920 --> 21:18.850
Do you think she can be an official?

21:22.160 --> 21:23.620
-You mean...
-You mean...

21:27.000 --> 21:27.720
Fan Yun.

21:38.030 --> 21:38.750
I know.

21:40.440 --> 21:41.400
Mr. Zheng

21:41.400 --> 21:43.420
controls the government affairs
all year round,

21:43.420 --> 21:44.220
all because of

21:44.350 --> 21:47.280
the old system
that has existed since ancient times.

21:48.400 --> 21:50.660
But now those old rules are full of flaws.

21:52.070 --> 21:53.130
At the morning assembly,

21:53.130 --> 21:54.460
it's full of old fogeys.

21:54.860 --> 21:56.860
Not to mention the lack of talents.

21:57.920 --> 21:59.240
For commoners, to be promoted

21:59.240 --> 22:00.340
is even more hopeless.

22:00.340 --> 22:02.070
Any power contrary to Mr. Zheng

22:02.530 --> 22:04.330
will be ruthlessly suppressed.

22:05.590 --> 22:06.800
This is what caused

22:07.250 --> 22:08.690
his dominance today.

22:10.240 --> 22:12.070
The matter of repairing
the ancestral temple

22:12.070 --> 22:13.070
is a good example.

22:13.440 --> 22:14.900
You are absolutely right.

22:15.310 --> 22:15.880
Even though we are

22:15.880 --> 22:17.540
from the Nine Noble Families,

22:17.970 --> 22:19.300
this situation

22:19.330 --> 22:21.280
is really shocking.

22:21.300 --> 22:23.020
We have to find a way after all.

22:24.110 --> 22:25.680
Have you had a plan already?

22:26.590 --> 22:28.960
I have always wanted
to promote commoners to be officials,

22:28.960 --> 22:31.220
to break the inherent selection system.

22:32.030 --> 22:34.630
But I have never found
a suitable opportunity.

22:35.440 --> 22:36.990
Now Fan Yun's ability

22:37.390 --> 22:38.310
and charisma

22:39.460 --> 22:41.020
is indeed a breakthrough.

22:43.440 --> 22:44.070
But...

22:45.240 --> 22:47.300
Nine Cities has long had a clear rule.

22:47.980 --> 22:50.030
To prevent relatives of the royal family
from seizing power,

22:50.030 --> 22:52.490
Her Ladyship can't be an official
under any circumstances.

22:52.490 --> 22:54.350
If Fan Yun wants to be an official,

22:55.310 --> 22:56.720
she can only...

23:02.130 --> 23:02.810
Divorce me.

23:04.590 --> 23:05.180
Yes.

23:24.100 --> 23:25.100
Your Excellency.

23:25.130 --> 23:27.060
I said leave me alone for a while.

23:28.040 --> 23:28.870
Fan Yun?

23:29.630 --> 23:30.720
Why are you here?

23:30.740 --> 23:32.260
I waited all night,

23:32.290 --> 23:33.860
but you didn't summon me.

23:34.140 --> 23:35.750
I had to come here myself.

23:36.970 --> 23:37.900
Your Excellency,

23:37.900 --> 23:39.650
about your trip
to the Zheng Residence today,

23:39.650 --> 23:40.540
how was it?

23:42.960 --> 23:44.120
I have expressed

23:44.140 --> 23:45.350
what I should.

23:46.070 --> 23:47.420
When we can do this much,

23:48.110 --> 23:50.970
Mr. Zheng's wariness
can also be mostly dispelled.

23:51.290 --> 23:51.990
It's also time

23:51.990 --> 23:53.050
to take a step back.

23:54.860 --> 23:55.930
Then why do you

23:55.960 --> 23:58.040
still look so depressed?

24:00.480 --> 24:02.030
These submitted memorials

24:02.710 --> 24:04.640
used to be shown to Mr. Zheng first.

24:05.100 --> 24:06.230
When they came to me,

24:06.370 --> 24:08.720
I only needed to draw a circle
and stamp them.

24:08.720 --> 24:10.850
But now that Mr. Zheng claims to be ill,

24:10.900 --> 24:11.890
all the memorials

24:11.890 --> 24:12.890
are piled up here.

24:13.560 --> 24:14.630
The task is heavy.

24:18.160 --> 24:18.840
Fan Yun.

24:19.970 --> 24:22.100
Why don't you share the burden with me?

24:24.510 --> 24:25.270
Me?

24:26.120 --> 24:27.330
Is it appropriate?

24:27.480 --> 24:28.200
It's fine.

24:28.990 --> 24:30.120
Just stay beside me

24:30.300 --> 24:31.430
and keep me company.

24:34.400 --> 24:35.070
Okay.

24:36.160 --> 24:38.640
Then I'll continue to help you

24:38.960 --> 24:40.800
sort out

24:40.820 --> 24:42.350
these official documents.

24:57.060 --> 24:58.480
Please wait a moment, everyone.

24:58.480 --> 25:00.200
The sesame flatbread will be ready soon.

25:00.200 --> 25:01.330
You go ahead and buy.

25:03.220 --> 25:04.750
One, two, three, four, five.

25:04.750 --> 25:06.340
You... you go first.

25:15.060 --> 25:15.740
Gao Ran!

25:20.160 --> 25:20.680
I...

25:25.930 --> 25:26.780
Miss Wei.

25:28.810 --> 25:30.670
Has Ling'an City become so small?

25:31.240 --> 25:32.600
It's not that Ling'an City has changed.

25:32.600 --> 25:34.830
It's the people living in it
that have changed.

25:34.830 --> 25:37.270
Is this what the playbooks call

25:37.290 --> 25:38.950
the fate written for mortals?

25:41.730 --> 25:43.400
If there's nothing else,

25:43.490 --> 25:45.090
I'll go back to the end of the line.

25:45.090 --> 25:45.790
No,

25:46.030 --> 25:47.200
y-you can just wait here.

25:47.200 --> 25:47.810
But

25:47.840 --> 25:49.010
can you help me

25:49.040 --> 25:49.960
buy some more?

25:50.960 --> 25:52.830
Are you really here to buy the flatbread?

25:52.830 --> 25:53.640
Really.

25:53.660 --> 25:54.550
What else?

25:55.200 --> 25:56.550
I heard Fan Yun say

25:56.960 --> 25:58.160
that Lord Fan Qi

25:58.160 --> 25:59.960
craves their sesame flatbread.

26:00.880 --> 26:02.240
I just received a letter from home,

26:02.240 --> 26:04.000
so I thought I'd ask someone
to bring some back.

26:04.000 --> 26:04.750
Let them know

26:04.750 --> 26:06.000
I'm living well here,

26:06.000 --> 26:07.330
so they'll feel better.

26:09.650 --> 26:11.380
So you have a side like this too.

26:22.380 --> 26:22.940
Wei Qiao,

26:23.000 --> 26:24.000
I'm a little thirsty.

26:24.000 --> 26:25.920
Can you go buy some mung bean soup for me?

26:25.920 --> 26:27.640
Didn't you just drink some?

26:29.620 --> 26:30.730
I'm still thirsty.

26:31.240 --> 26:32.500
You're thirsty again?

26:47.110 --> 26:48.880
Miss Wei, your hand...

26:50.790 --> 26:52.010
Was it injured in a fight?

26:52.010 --> 26:52.650
No.

26:53.140 --> 26:54.410
But that's not important.

26:54.410 --> 26:55.600
What's important is that

26:55.600 --> 26:57.150
someone gave me some wound medicine,

26:57.150 --> 26:58.610
so it healed very quickly.

27:00.360 --> 27:01.890
So someone cares about you.

27:05.360 --> 27:06.600
You care about me?

27:06.620 --> 27:08.550
Why would it be me caring about you?

27:08.830 --> 27:09.680
You just said

27:09.680 --> 27:11.200
the medicine was given by someone
who cares about me.

27:11.200 --> 27:12.660
I asked Ying this morning,

27:12.770 --> 27:14.370
and he said he didn't send it.

27:14.580 --> 27:16.440
That still doesn't prove it's me.

27:16.700 --> 27:17.730
Still won't admit it?

27:17.730 --> 27:19.430
This is specially supplied
to the Guardian Corps.

27:19.430 --> 27:20.690
How could it not be you?

27:21.840 --> 27:22.490
It wasn't me.

27:22.490 --> 27:23.170
Was it?

27:23.270 --> 27:23.920
It really wasn't.

27:23.920 --> 27:24.720
It was you.

27:24.720 --> 27:25.510
It really wasn't me.

27:25.510 --> 27:26.200
It was, it was.

27:26.200 --> 27:26.960
It really wasn't me.

27:26.960 --> 27:28.030
How could it not be?

27:28.880 --> 27:29.310
They're ready.

27:29.310 --> 27:30.240
I'll go buy some.

27:34.550 --> 27:35.280
That's fine.

27:35.530 --> 27:36.790
We have plenty of time.

28:36.790 --> 28:37.790
Your Excellency.

28:38.720 --> 28:40.380
What were you thinking about?

28:46.030 --> 28:46.720
Fan Yun.

28:48.440 --> 28:49.240
What's wrong?

28:49.630 --> 28:51.680
Your tone is so serious all of a sudden.

28:51.680 --> 28:53.480
It sounds quite scary.

28:53.510 --> 28:54.310
Let me ask you,

28:55.740 --> 28:58.160
the path of an official
is fraught with difficulties

28:58.160 --> 28:59.620
and extremely dangerous.

28:59.700 --> 29:01.180
Mr. Zheng is a visible one.

29:01.960 --> 29:03.960
There are many invisible obstacles.

29:03.960 --> 29:04.750
In this case,

29:06.310 --> 29:08.240
do you still want to be an official?

29:09.200 --> 29:09.880
I do.

29:12.100 --> 29:13.690
To be able to contribute

29:13.720 --> 29:15.450
to the people of the Nine Cities

29:16.160 --> 29:17.820
has always been my dream.

29:21.740 --> 29:24.070
But to be an official,
you must divorce me.

29:24.550 --> 29:26.210
Are you still willing to do it?

29:32.610 --> 29:33.690
I am willing.

29:47.530 --> 29:48.610
Do you know

29:50.830 --> 29:52.890
that I have long been in love with you?

29:59.000 --> 30:00.200
Your Excellency...

30:03.230 --> 30:04.120
I...

30:11.290 --> 30:11.850
I...

30:11.950 --> 30:15.090
♪ Watch how many flowers
bloom and wither ♪

30:15.510 --> 30:18.940
♪ Count how many springs
and autumns pass ♪

30:19.310 --> 30:21.870
♪ Why the sighs and regrets? ♪

30:27.930 --> 30:31.420
♪ Lovers wait a lifetime ♪

30:31.980 --> 30:35.170
♪ Feelings that can't be severed ♪

30:35.920 --> 30:38.670
♪ How to let go? ♪

30:42.030 --> 30:43.070
Since you want to,

30:44.170 --> 30:47.520
♪ All our fates were long inscribed ♪

30:44.750 --> 30:45.960
I will allow you

30:46.840 --> 30:48.000
to be my official.

30:47.860 --> 30:51.520
♪ How to set free grief and joy? ♪

30:51.290 --> 30:52.290
No taking back moves

30:52.090 --> 30:53.810
♪ Mortal life is but an ephemeral dream ♪

30:53.500 --> 30:54.460
once played.

30:54.220 --> 30:59.770
♪ No mortal soul may rule its life ♪

31:00.150 --> 31:01.640
♪ If women are akin to blossoms ♪

31:01.680 --> 31:04.020
♪ Can they be cherished tenderly? ♪

31:04.180 --> 31:07.350
♪ For whom do they hide tears silently? ♪

31:07.630 --> 31:09.850
♪ How could one bear to lay blame? ♪

31:09.870 --> 31:12.240
♪ Time runs wild with reckless haste ♪

31:12.270 --> 31:15.970
♪ Never mind that
fate dyes pureness crimson red ♪

31:16.280 --> 31:17.620
♪ For whom does ♪

31:17.640 --> 31:19.810
♪ This phoenix blossom bloom? ♪

31:19.840 --> 31:23.810
♪ Love fills my years,
and my heart remains true ♪

31:24.040 --> 31:26.090
♪ Let all worldly longing fade away ♪

31:26.120 --> 31:28.510
♪ Fall deep within a single dream ♪

31:28.650 --> 31:33.560
♪ Wait till a breath of wind arrives ♪

31:33.860 --> 31:35.350
♪ If women are akin to blossoms ♪

31:35.390 --> 31:37.730
♪ Can they be cherished tenderly? ♪

31:37.890 --> 31:41.060
♪ For whom do they hide tears silently? ♪

31:41.340 --> 31:43.560
♪ How could one bear to lay blame? ♪

31:43.580 --> 31:45.950
♪ Time runs wild with reckless haste ♪

31:45.980 --> 31:49.680
♪ Never mind that
fate dyes pureness crimson red ♪

31:49.990 --> 31:51.330
♪ For whom does ♪

31:51.350 --> 31:53.520
♪ This phoenix blossom bloom? ♪

31:53.550 --> 31:57.520
♪ Love fills my years,
and my heart remains true ♪

31:57.750 --> 31:59.800
♪ Let all worldly longing fade away ♪

31:59.830 --> 32:02.220
♪ Fall deep within a single dream ♪

32:02.540 --> 32:13.550
♪ Wait till a breath of wind arrives ♪

32:33.550 --> 32:34.550
Your Excellency,

32:34.870 --> 32:35.870
how do you feel?

32:35.890 --> 32:37.350
I feel refreshed all over.

32:38.320 --> 32:38.850
And then?

32:38.870 --> 32:39.740
And then,

32:40.230 --> 32:40.950
continue.

32:40.970 --> 32:41.490
Come on.

32:41.520 --> 32:41.890
Okay.

32:44.030 --> 32:44.750
Fan Yun,

32:45.410 --> 32:47.090
how dare you!

32:48.010 --> 32:48.810
What's wrong?

32:48.840 --> 32:49.760
Did I hurt you?

32:50.310 --> 32:51.180
No.

32:51.210 --> 32:51.900
Then...

32:52.900 --> 32:54.750
I'm just cooperating with you.

32:55.070 --> 32:55.930
Come on, continue.

32:55.930 --> 32:56.820
Hurry, hurry.

32:56.850 --> 32:57.570
Continue.

32:57.690 --> 32:59.860
How dare you challenge my bottom line!

32:59.960 --> 33:00.340
Right?

33:00.340 --> 33:01.610
W-What...

33:01.640 --> 33:02.170
what bottom line

33:02.170 --> 33:03.910
did I challenge?

33:04.600 --> 33:06.070
I just hate your face!

33:06.440 --> 33:07.570
This face of yours!

33:07.760 --> 33:08.710
Look at you!

33:08.730 --> 33:09.860
Your eyes may be big,

33:09.880 --> 33:11.200
but they're lifeless!

33:11.200 --> 33:12.310
Your brows may arch high,

33:12.310 --> 33:13.690
but they're arrogant and overbearing!

33:13.690 --> 33:15.040
And your nose!

33:15.680 --> 33:17.240
It's straight,

33:17.260 --> 33:18.380
but looks suspicious!

33:18.380 --> 33:19.310
What should we do?

33:19.310 --> 33:20.510
It's all just a game of pretense.

33:20.510 --> 33:22.000
I think you just said

33:22.000 --> 33:23.010
everything on your mind.

33:23.010 --> 33:23.950
No, I didn't.

33:24.050 --> 33:24.780
Yes, you did.

33:25.400 --> 33:26.120
Let me do it.

33:26.140 --> 33:26.870
Listen to me.

33:27.160 --> 33:27.690
Do you...

33:28.130 --> 33:30.400
do you think I want to be your wife?

33:30.420 --> 33:31.260
Hurry, hurry.

33:31.350 --> 33:32.240
But since you don't like it,

33:32.240 --> 33:34.140
why did you marry into the residence?

33:34.140 --> 33:34.940
Go back then.

33:35.290 --> 33:36.400
I... I...

33:36.430 --> 33:38.390
I'll go back then!

33:38.420 --> 33:40.200
You think I don't want to go back?

33:40.200 --> 33:42.290
Ever since I married you,

33:42.320 --> 33:43.470
I've been

33:43.490 --> 33:44.660
either poisoned

33:44.720 --> 33:45.440
or

33:45.440 --> 33:46.560
kidnapped.

33:46.590 --> 33:49.270
Y-You're not a man at all!

33:49.400 --> 33:50.350
You're just

33:50.350 --> 33:51.200
a coward!

33:51.370 --> 33:52.520
What you just said

33:52.810 --> 33:54.540
are your true feelings, right?

33:55.960 --> 33:57.540
They aren't my true feelings at all.

33:57.540 --> 33:59.390
I was just making things up.

34:00.200 --> 34:00.990
Your Excellency,

34:00.990 --> 34:02.100
your health is important.

34:02.100 --> 34:04.150
Please don't let anger ruin your health.

34:04.150 --> 34:05.500
Who let you in?

34:06.330 --> 34:08.699
Look how fierce he is.

34:08.920 --> 34:10.429
He scared me to death.

34:10.870 --> 34:11.969
Calm down, Your Excellency.

34:11.969 --> 34:13.320
Her Ladyship meant no harm.

34:13.320 --> 34:14.429
She even came all the way here

34:14.429 --> 34:15.560
to bring you a midnight snack.

34:15.560 --> 34:16.159
Yeah.

34:16.550 --> 34:17.320
What a—

34:17.320 --> 34:18.250
Midnight snack?

34:18.840 --> 34:19.370
Alright.

34:20.659 --> 34:21.219
Look.

34:21.630 --> 34:23.420
Look what she made.

34:23.440 --> 34:24.030
Is this...

34:24.030 --> 34:25.030
for humans to eat?

34:26.969 --> 34:29.900
My good intentions
are completely misunderstood.

34:29.929 --> 34:31.000
Scold me. Scold me.

34:31.020 --> 34:31.960
Scold me.

34:31.980 --> 34:32.940
Scold me.

34:32.969 --> 34:34.500
You are an attendant, right?

34:34.500 --> 34:35.480
Write this down.

34:35.920 --> 34:37.179
She's good at cooking,

34:37.350 --> 34:38.830
but what she made tonight

34:38.850 --> 34:40.310
is comparable to pig slop!

34:40.590 --> 34:41.429
Well,

34:41.449 --> 34:43.739
this is not for me to record.

34:44.870 --> 34:46.460
What should I do?

34:46.489 --> 34:48.730
I'm too ashamed to see anyone.

34:49.400 --> 34:50.730
I'm going back.

34:50.909 --> 34:53.270
I'm going back to my father.

34:55.210 --> 34:57.560
Going home to my father.

35:05.440 --> 35:06.970
Write it down word for word,

35:07.510 --> 35:08.610
or you'll lose your head.

35:08.610 --> 35:09.340
Yes.

35:09.370 --> 35:10.290
Yes, yes, yes.
